    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ceremonial chains worn to signify membership in a specific guild or order; often incorporating various forms of links and shields or plates. They may be attached to a textile support.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
